February 13,2020
The A2N epidemic volunteer group initiated one of the in-depth content projects
"memory of tomorrow" online photo exhibition

Freeze time with the camera
To record the day's joys and sorrows
To give tomorrow the strength to move on

Before you know it, it's stage two
The contribution works of the little friends are more and more unique
Many moving moments are recorded in a unique way

A total of 13 entries were selected in the second phase
The duration of the exhibition is unlimited
Please arrange your own viewing time
